column5: Thought I 'd share some photos from my friends hunt, pics are of my brother, he shot the large buck, Stopped by from some post hunt drinks and these were hanging from the trees, I don't hunt myself but nonetheless, some good times
Nice job! I count 9, lots of meat in the freezer. Where does he hunt?
Hell......it don't get no better than that......  ...my season has been a disaster so far.
Any deer's a good deer. Good job.

Were they hunting in the Fort Frances area?  I was getting  breakfast at McDonald's this past week and ran into a bunch of guys stopped in Thunder Bay on their way back home who had I think 10 deer stacked up like cordwood in the back of a truck and trailer. I said, "let me guess, Fort Frances", answer, yup!!!!
The count was 10 actually, hunting in haldimand though
